Author: ccedk_pr
Title: [ANN][ICO] genEOS - Blockchain 4.0 for business
Body: Insolvency, cargo damage, tax evasion, and underinsurance - these are only some of the risks that the logistics industry faces.  But there is a solution - blockchain.  With the help of its distributed ledgers and smart contracts, blockchain can considerably reduce these risks.  There are some companies that are already unlocking the blockchain efficiency for logistics. For instance, IBM and Maersk developed the solution tracking the cargo along its way. This software allows all the stakeholders to view the progress and check up all the documents associated with the shipment. Author: ccedk_pr
Title: [ANN][ICO] genEOS - Blockchain 4.0 for business
Body: How Blockchain Can Help Us Stop Fearing IoT  As for today, no efficient solution for IoT vulnerabilities has been found. Producing complex chips, running thousands of tests prior to manufacturing, authenticating and encrypting data, releasing updates and forcing backups on a frequent basis are expensive yet fairly weak measures that the industry have come up with so far.  Blockchain is capable of providing a previously unknown data security level. To put it short, blockchain can decentralize an IoT firmware network, taking the authority from its center and distributing it across the devices. Author: geneos_io
Title: [ANN][ICO] genEOS - Blockchain 4.0 for business
Body: Blockchain technology has been evolving rapidly - from the originally slow Bitcoin protocol to the third generation of blockchain with much higher scalability and speed. Each generation of blockchain has its own distinguishing features that determine its usability and integrability into business processes.  At genEOS, we aim to create a blockchain 4.0 that overcomes obstacles faced by previous generations, yet maintaining their major improvements and advantages, and delivers blockchain as a business-usable environment for creating and running applications, bringing the technology fully mainstream. We believe that a blockchain 4.0 environment should have the following features:  very low latency of transactions and the potential for parallel performance across multiple CPUs, for rapid function and unlimited scaling  delegated Proof of Stake structure for producing new blocks, to create a blockchain structure that maximizes real-world decentralization  exponentially accelerated processing and transaction speeds that enable to create a platform that lets Dapps rival standard web apps for speed and versatility, while maintaining the unique security and other advantages of blockchain technology  an operating system-like construct upon which applications can be built. It provides accounts, authentication, databases, asynchronous communication and the scheduling of applications across multiple CPU cores and/or clusters   Seele may have its own vision of blockchain 4.0 as it is determined by the project’s creators.  To find out what differences and similarities the two projects have, please visit the official genEOS website geneos.io.  We will be happy to answer any other questions you may have about genEOS.

Author: ccedk_pr
Title: [ANN][ICO] genEOS - Blockchain 4.0 for business
Body: View on Github :: Read Whitepaper :: Visit Site  WHY GENEOS?  LEGAL FRAMEWORK, FAIR AND TRANSPARENT TOKEN DISTRIBUTION  genEOS exploits an innovative model to achieve transparent and fair token distribution. A US-based non-profit organization will administer the funds generated and manage the token distribution process, securing legal and regulatory compliance and ensuring the genEOS project is transparent and a great opportunity for business.  ANOTHER CHANCE TO GET INVOLVED  genEOS is a fully-fledged blockchain ecosystem, based on a distributed network that is currently redefining expectations of the technology’s capabilities. Seize your second chance to join a project with the vast scope for business adoption and utilization, with fair participation costs immune to market volatility.  CREATING AND LAUNCHING DECENTRALIZED APPLICATIONS  The genEOS platform opens up the possibility to further develop, create and launch your own business products on the platform, using its computational and storage capacity. You can also rent out that capacity to third parties. Join genEOS to set up your own project, offer that opportunity to clients and partners, or hire our 60+-strong team of blockchain experts who are ready to build business-critical Dapps for you.  BLOCKCHAIN 4.0: EXPONENTIALLY IMPROVED  The genEOS project leverages the power of EOS software, utilizing its exponentially accelerated processing and transaction speeds to create a platform that lets Dapps rival standard web apps for speed and versatility, while maintaining the unique security and other advantages of blockchain technology. Constant updates and cooperation with the EOS technical and development teams help ensure the project’s success.  KEY FEATURES  TRULY DECENTRALIZED  genEOS uses a dPoS (delegated Proof of Stake) structure for producing new blocks, to create a blockchain structure that maximizes real-world decentralization.  HIGH PERFORMANCE  The genEOS blockchain is characterized by very low latency of transactions and the potential for parallel performance across multiple CPUs, for rapid function and unlimited scaling.  FULLY OPEN-SOURCE  The code that powers the genEOS blockchain structure is fully open-source and available on GitHub for developers to consult and use to build your own Dapps.  BUSINESS FOCUSED  The genEOS blockchain is business-oriented by design, offering businesses multiple monetization options and application development opportunities on the same rapid and secure blockchain architecture.  INNOVATIVE ARCHITECTURE & SMART CONTRACTS  The innovative structure of the genEOS blockchain allows a new block to be produced every 0.5 seconds. Self-executing smart contracts can be created and added to the blockchain, essentially in limitless numbers and real time.  BUILT ON TOP OF EOS SOFTWARE  EOS software provides an operating system-like construct upon which applications can be built. The software provides accounts, authentication, databases, asynchronous communication and the scheduling of applications across multiple CPU cores and/or clusters.  Lear more abour our technical team, advisory partner and founding partner.  Find us on socials  Twitter :: Telegram :: Reddit :: Medium  News and articles:  https://dex.openledger.io/openledger-partners-with-geneos-to-offer-blockchain-4-0-for-enterprise/  https://news.bitcoin.com/pr-geneos-blockchain-4-0-for-business-announced-crowdsale-is-launched/
